      <title>五角大楼部署舰艇和战斗机以增强中东存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/pentagon-deploying-ships-fighters-to-add-to-mideast-presence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列面临伊朗报复暗杀哈马斯和真主党领导人的威胁，五角大楼正通过派遣舰艇、战斗机和弹道导弹防御舰来加强其在中东的存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/pentagon-deploying-ships-fighters-to-add-to-mideast-presence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 22:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
